column1: This document provides a list of Authorised Firms, it does not supersede the Financial Service Register which should be referred to as the most accurate and up to date source of information.

This list of firms includes Legal Entity Identifier (LEI) data. For more information see the Firm Data section at https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/prudential-regulation/authorisations/which-firms-does-the-pra-regulate
